{"tid":1570032,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[分析]對家點解出動咁大人力物力周圍拆牆","createTime":"2019-09-15T01:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:58:50.000Z","uid":34816,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a02ab0d8eb27fda4d92e0598c1d2ee203bfe54","tid":1570032,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:04:49.000Z","msg":"除左已經有既論點如引起衝突拉人，試圖減弱運動宣傳力外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外一個重要原因係因為臨近蝈慶啊，共黨一定想不惜化價製造一片歌舞昇平既假像</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n可以想像得到愈近十月一，共黨既清理行動會愈趨瘋狂，但我可以係到大大聲同港共講，我地香港人一撚定會同你好好慶祝你既蝈慶（或者叫亡黨日都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我地可以點應對？由即日開始每個人身上都帶上最新既文宣圖，實行行到邊痴到邊，睇下係你班愛蝈人士拆得快定我地全香港人起得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c165534f8a4ea67eb8378ca2bf2fce558b8a24a7","tid":1570032,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:06:01.000Z","msg":"陣間港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa1a9f9733f0268e44cf6c2620ba6006f6634aa","tid":1570032,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2175d499ff6891a4ca3c62a7c51bf28f88223477","tid":1570032,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c165534f8a4ea67eb8378ca2bf2fce558b8a24a7","tid":1570032,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:06:01.000Z","msg":"陣間港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bec518e273eb0017604cea3ac3e56661ec1a60","tid":1570032,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"港共：你班仆街周圍貼我邊有位掛國慶BANNER啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"